My sister, “What is the bondage?”, because

01:44:34.750 --> 01:44:44.180
I remember the song, but didn’t remember
the exact words, you see.

01:44:44.180 --> 01:44:48.540
Just now she told Me.

01:44:48.540 --> 01:45:02.630
And she is another great, great singer, Roshnara
Begum, and the way she was singing, you know,

01:45:02.630 --> 01:45:12.560
as if the whole Puria - the whole building
of Puria she made it manifest – really.

01:45:12.560 --> 01:45:15.960
She made it manifest – the whole Puria raga.

01:45:15.960 --> 01:45:27.460
Say, such a beautiful thing and that is what
it is that here is a sign of a person who

01:45:27.460 --> 01:45:46.280
has done it so much with that purity of raga,
is the point - the purity of raga.

01:45:46.280 --> 01:46:23.260
And it’s very good for Sahaja Yogis to know
that the purity of understanding of that

01:46:23.260 --> 01:46:35.239
if you go a little bit this side, a little
bit this side you get away from Sushumna.

